entity.name: South Africa’s former president, FW de Klerk, has died at 85
entity.description: FW de Klerk was head of state between September 1989 and May 1994. A key figure in the South Africa's transition to democracy, he had been diagnosed with cancer this year. A statement from the FW de Klerk Foundation on Thursday morning read: "Former President FW de Klerk died peacefully at his home in Fresnaye (Cape Town) earlier this morning following his struggle against mesothelioma cancer."

This morning I will be responding to questions raised by members of the House of People’s Representatives. 

Watch the responses live: 

https://t.co/gC3Aqi8xhv
የኢትዮጵያ የርህራሄ ተምሳሌት የነበሩት አበበች ጎበናን እልፈተ ህይወት በመስማቴ እጅግ አዝኛለሁ:: ለቤተሰቦቻቸው: ለወዳጆቻቸው እና በሕይወታቸው ላይ ተጽዕኖ ለነበራቸው ሁሉ ከልብ መፅናናትን እመኛለሁ፡፡
ኢትዮጵያውያን ከፖለቲካ ይልቅ ሀገር ትቀድማለች የሚል መርሕ አንገበው ሰላማዊና ዴሞክራሲያዊ ምርጫ በማካሄድ ሀገራቸውን አሸናፊ አድርገዋታል። 2/2 https://t.co/67K7Jz6Ka7
የሲቪክ ማኅበራት ደርጅቶች ምክር ቤት በዘንድሮው ምርጫ ለተፎካከሩ የፖለቲካ ፓርቲዎች ባዘጋጀው የምስጋና መርሐ ግብር ተካፍያለሁ:: ኢትዮጵያ ዘንድሮ ነጻና ዴሞክራሲያዊ ምርጫ ማካሄድ የቻለችው ሁላችንም ኢትዮጵያ እንድታሸንፍ በመሥራታችን ነው። 1/2 https://t.co/re3rD3tc2X
We also discussed their assessment of challenges and gaps that surfaced in the electoral process as lessons learnt to strengthen our nascent democracy. 2/2 https://t.co/X0NMEM2dc9

I met with political party heads this morning, a week after the 6th National Elections, to express my gratitude for their contribution in enabling a peaceful election in which #Ethiopia came out a winner. 1/2 https://t.co/OPXDOJoNyT

የአፍሪካ የአመራር ልህቀት አካዳሚን ዛሬ መርቀናል::

Today we inaugurated the African Leadership Excellence Academy. https://t.co/NBTZwYreKM
ባለፈው ሳምንት ለ6ኛው ብሔራዊ ምርጫ ሰኞ በሚዘጉ የመንግሥት መሥሪያ ቤቶች ምትክ ይህ ቅዳሜ የሥራ ቀን እንደሚሆን አሳውቀን ነበር፡፡ ስለሆነም ሁሉም የመንግሥት መሥሪያ ቤቶች ነገ ክፍት ሆነው አገልግሎት እንዲሰጡ አሳስባለሁ፡፡
He underlined that African issues remain under AU and parties should continue negotiation under the auspices of the AU. 2/2

I attended the AU Bureau meeting online session earlier today on GERD information sharing made by President @FelixUdps, Chairperson of the AU. The President said he will provide full report to the Bureau at appropriate time & discussion would be deferred to a later date. 1/2 https://t.co/TelNDAR6Ub
ከጠቅላላ ሂደቱ ጋር የተያያዙ ደካማ እና ጠንካራ ጎኖችን ለማየት ሞክረናል:: ኮሚቴው በሰላም እና ደኅነት ጉዳዮች እንዲሁም በቀጣይ መሠራት ባለባቸው ጉዳዮች ላይ አቅጣጫ አስቀምጧል:: 2/2
የብልጽግና ሥራ አስፈጻሚ ኮሚቴ የምርጫ ሂደት ግምገማ አድርጓል።  ግምገማው በቅድመ ምርጫ ዝግጅት፣ በምርጫ ክንውን፣ በሕዝብ ተሳትፎ እና በአጠቃላይ የምርጫው ሂደት ላይ ያተኮረ ነበር:: 1/2 https://t.co/ht61h3SioB

This morning I visited with impoverished households in the Aware area for our annual house renovations program. In this area we will renovate up to 15 households. I encourage all with the means to pool resources and engage in supporting fellow Ethiopians live a dignified life. https://t.co/GHY7qsTDu9

Ahead of the 2nd filling, Ethiopia is releasing more water from last year storage through newly completed outlets & sharing information. The next filling takes place only during heavy rainfall months of July/August, ensuring benefits in reducing floods in Sudan.

Ethiopia, in developing Abbay River for its needs, has no intention of causing harm to lower riparian countries. data.text: Work to #RebuildTigray has commenced with teams on the ground undertaking repair work on damaged infrastructure to restore essential services. Our humanitarian assistance efforts will also continue strengthened to attend to the vulnerable. We will restore, rebuild and develop.

In today’s discussions with political parties and CSOs, we reached an understanding on ways to ensure the 2021 elections are democratic.
I shared the federal government’s unwavering efforts to lay the foundation for free & fair elections in #Ethiopia. https://t.co/294P1yp2Ab

Duty to country entails finishing what we started and staying the course of what we’ve planned. The remarkable history of #Ethiopia shows us that despite all odds, this great nation continues to prevail. 

#EthiopiaPrevails https://t.co/54bapk3jsW

This morning I will be responding to questions raised by members of the House of People’s Representatives. 

Watch the responses live.  https://t.co/jRmH8rWllV

I am pleased to share that we have completed and ceased the military operations in the #Tigray region. 

Our focus now will be on rebuilding the region and providing humanitarian assistance while Federal Police apprehend the TPLF clique.

ይህ ግን ለዚህ ጁንታ የመጨረሻው ነው። ጥንቃቄያችን 'ሙት ይዞን እንዳይሞት' ነው። መፍጠን አለብን፤ የተረፉትን ለመታደግና ግፍ የተፈጸመባቸውንም ለዓለም ለማጋለጥ።

አላወቁም ከአልማዝ የጠነከረች መሆኗን። ዓላማው ሠራዊታችንንና ሕዝቡን አስቆጥቶ ለበቀል ርምጃ ማነሣሣት ነው። አላወቁም ልበ ሰፊ ሕዝብና ሠራዊት እንዳለን። 
በየቦታው ስንደርስ ከዚህ የከፋ ጭካኔና ግፍ ሊገጥመን ይችላል። 2/4
ለስግብግቡ ጁንታ ግፍ እስትንፋሱ፣ ጭካኔ ነፍሱ ነው። ጀግናው የመከላከያ ሠራዊታችን ሽራሮን ሲቆጣጠር፣ እጅና እግራቸውን የፊጥኝ ታሥረው የተረሸኑ የመከላከያ አባላትን አግኝቷል። ጭካኔው ልብ ሰባሪ ነበር። ዓላማው ኢትዮጵያን መስበር ነው። 1/4

ስግብግቡና አረመኔው የመቀሌ ጁንታ በሰሜን ኮማንድ አባላት ያደረሰውን ኢሰብአዊ ግድያ፣ ግፍ እና በደል መቸውንም አንረሳውም። ይህ ጁንታ ለፍትህ ቀርቦ ተገቢውን ቅጣት  ሳይገኝ ለአፍታም ቢሆን አናርፍም። 1/2

Our law enforcement operations in Tigray are proceeding as planned: operations will cease as soon as the criminal junta is disarmed, legitimate administration in the region restored, and fugitives apprehended & brought to justice — all of them rapidly coming within reach.

data.text: My congratulations to US President-Elect @JoeBiden and Vice President-Elect @KamalaHarris on your historic #Election2020 win. #Ethiopia looks forward to working closely with you.

Ethiopia’s quest to have a successful transition towards constitutional democracy requires adherence to rule of law. The Government will continue to take necessary law enforcement measures to safeguard & advance our nascent process of democratization from rogue political actors.

Criminal elements cannot escape the rule of law under the guise of seeking reconciliation and a call for dialogue. Our operation aims to end the impunity that has prevailed for far too long and hold accountable individuals and groups under the laws of the land.

Ethiopia has no place for criminal elements. The proud Ethiopian people of Tigray & other citizens cannot be taken hostage by fugitives from justice forever. We shall extract the region of these criminal elements & relaunch our country on a path to sustainable prosperity for all.

Article 51 of FDRE Constitution, listing powers & functions of federal gov’t stipulates that “It shall protect & defend the Constitution”. To discharge this duty the gov’t is taking measures to enforce the rule of law against a clique that attacked our National Defense Forces.1/2

The Federal Gov patiently tried for several months to resolve differences with TPLF leadership peacefully; we tried mediation, reconciliation, dialogue. All failed b/c of TPLF criminal hubris & intransigence. In the last straw TPLF attacked the Northern Command based in Tigray2/2

Operations by federal defence forces underway in Northern #Ethiopia have clear, limited & achievable objectives — to restore the rule of law & the constitutional order, and to safeguard the rights of Ethiopians to lead a peaceful life wherever they are in the country.1/2

በኢትዮጵያውያን ላይ እየተፈጸመ ባለው ማንነትን መሠረት ባደረገው ጥቃት እጅግ ማዘኔን እገልፃለሁ። 

የኢትዮጵያ ጠላቶች፤ "ወይ እኛ እንገዛለን፤ ወይ ሀገር አትኖርም" ብለው ተነሥተዋል። ለዚህም የጥፋት ዐቅማቸውን ሁሉ እየተጠቀሙ ነው። https://t.co/YyF6AZwDrL

data.text: Our ambition of planting 20billion seedlings in four years is halfway complete. In 2021’s #GreenLegacy we aim to go regional. Together with Lt. Gen. Al-Burhan we visited Joytech Seedlings Nursery based in Bishoftu to see their nursery and their export standard vegetable produce. https://t.co/x8mlw8uybT

The people of Ethiopia and Sudan have strong relations rooted in culture and history. Together with General Al-Burhan in Adama, we received blessings from Abba Gada’s for  strengthened ties. We further honor his presence by gifting him the horse and armor of peace warriors. https://t.co/2nIHiNV46u

https://t.co/ZBYH8ju1np

Currently in discussions with high level Federal officials and regional presidents on national issues. Key items on the agenda include national peace and security concerns as well as response to natural disasters. https://t.co/xAstPr02nB
Through the government's efforts further damage has been prevented. We will provide appropriate support to local farmers affected by the desert locusts. 2/2 https://t.co/DEDtW9l6XQ
As we conclude the day’s development project visits, we observed the damage caused by desert locust swarm in Goro Gutu Woreda, East Hararge Zone of Oromia regional state. 1/2 https://t.co/kfctnxFWzi
https://t.co/s0Rcd5srGc
I’m also quite pleased to have seen the residential houses, pedestrian walkways and green legacy trees planted, all within a short period of time. 2/2 https://t.co/0Cq0t3xmFd

The Dire Dawa Industrial Park Project we inaugurated today sits on 150ha with 15 sheds in the first phase of industry development. It offers youth in the community the opportunity to grasp new skills and knowledge as well as demonstrate their productivity. 1/2 https://t.co/fq8k80SZVo
This will not only enable it to earn foreign exchange by using the vast livestock resources in the area, but also help create jobs for the local community. 2/2 https://t.co/4FwFVgxam9

On the outskirts of Dire Dawa, we inaugurated an abattoir that has been set up to export animal meat products. Built 5 km from Dire Dawa, the abattoir has the capacity to slaughter more than 100 camels and more than 3,000 sheep and goats per day.1/2 https://t.co/BOr3BUUm1L

On the other hand, we also saw wheat and other crops being grown on 100,000 hectares of land in the same Aw Barre woreda. Although progress of 30 quintals per hectare is a good start, it is necessary to increase the productivity in the future. 2/2 https://t.co/TGwst4Prp0
We visited the damage caused by the locust swarm in the Somali region. The swarm is now under control through chemical sprays administered with aircrafts. 1/2 https://t.co/seETEoWHzS

The remaining 56 km road from Jijiga to Gelelesh was completed at a cost of 1 billion birr and was inaugurated today. The road is of great importance as it is the main development corridor of the region.2/2 https://t.co/v69dcEnPL1

tweets.text: A month ago we launched the campaign to increase #COVID19 testing throughout the country to inform measures that need to be taken in curbing the spread of the virus. 1/2
የአንድ ሀገር ብልጽግና ከማኅበራዊ ኃላፊነት መጎልበት ጋር ትሥሥር አለው።ማኅበራዊ ኃላፊነት ዝቅተኛ የሆነባቸው ሀገራት ለዕድገት ብዙ ማገዶ ይጨርሳሉ።የመሠልጠን ጉዟቸውም መሰናክል የሚገጥመው በዋናነት ኃላፊነት ከማይሰማቸው ዜጎቻቸው ነው።1/2

እንደ ኢትዮጵያ ብዝኃ ማንነት ባላቸው ሀገራት ዴሞክራሲን ጽኑ መሠረት ላይ ለመትከል ብቻ ሳይሆን የሀገር አንድነትን ለማጠናከር የወንድማማችነት ዕሴት እጅግ ወሳኝ ነው፡፡

ስለሆነም በሀገራችን የወንድማማችነት ዕሴት እንዲጎለብት 2/3
ስለ ዴሞክራሲ ግንባታ ስናስብ ቀድመው ወደ ጭንቅላታችን ከሚመጡት የነጻነትና የእኩልነት ዕሴቶች ባለፈ ሁላችንም የዘነጋነው ‹‹የወንድማማችነት ዕሴት›› ከምንም በላይ የተለየ ትኩረት ልንሰጠው የሚገባ ነው፡፡ 1/3
የምናደርገው ጉዞ፥ ሀብት፣ ጊዜና ጉልበት ከማባከን ውጭ ምንም ጥቅም አይኖረውም፡፡ አንድ ርምጃ ወደ መሐል ለመቅረብ የማይፈቅድ ፍላጎት እንኳን አንድ ሀገርን ቀርቶ አንድ ቤተሰብን አያቆምም። 2/3

እንደ ሀገር የጋራ ግብ ከያዝን የሀገራችን ህልውና ጠብቀን የጋራ ድል እንደምንቀዳጅ ምንም ጥርጥር የለውም፡፡

ለዚህ ደግሞ ሁለት ተቃራኒ ዋልታዎች ላይ የሚንጠለጠሉ ፍላጎቶቻችን መቀራረብ አለባቸው። እኔ ያልኩት ካልሆነ በሚል ግትርነት 1/3
ጽኑ መሪዎች ብሩህ ነጋችንን ይተልማሉ። ከነጠላ ጉዳይ ይልቅ ምሉዕ እይታን የሚያስቀድሙና ከችግር በላይ ከፍ ብለው መፍትሄ የሚያፈልቁ ዜጎች ውድ የሀገር ሀብቶች ናቸው። 2/3

ብልጽግና ጉዟችን ለሀገራችንን ትርጉም ያለው ለውጥ ከማሳካት በዘለለ ብቁ መሪዎችን ለማፍራት ይተጋል።

እንደ ንስር የሩቁን የሚመለከቱ፤ ከዋናው ዓላማቸው ሳይዛነፉ ግባቸውን የሚመቱ፤ በትጋት አሻራቸውን አኑረው የሚያልፉ  1/3
ግባችን ለሁሉም ሕዝብ ብሩህ ቀን እንዲመጣለት ማስቻል ነው። እንዳንዱ ዜጋ በሀገሩ ደስታን፣ በሀገሩ ምቾትን፣ በሀገሩ ተስፋን እንዲጨብጥ የማድረግ ጉዟችን የማለዳዋን ጸሐይ ተከትሎ ሙቀትና ፍካቱ እየጨመረ ብሩህ የሆነው 2/3
የብልጽግና መንገድ የማለዳውን ጀምበር ተከትሎ እየፈካ መጥቷል። የብርሃን ጸዳሎቹ ሙቀትና ፍካትን እያጎለበቱ ለብዙዎች ተስፋን መፈንጠቃቸውን ቀጥለዋል። ዓላማችን ለእያንዳንዱ ኢትዮጵያዊ ንጋትን ማብሰር ነው፡፡ 1/3
ጠንክሮ መሥራት እና በትጋት ላይ የተመሠረተ ጠንካራ የሥራ ሥነ ምግባር  የስኬት ምሦሶ ነው። በመስቀል አደባባይ የሚካሄደውን ሥራ በወቅቱ ለማጠናቀቅ ሌት እና ቀን ለሚሠሩ ወንዶች እና ሴቶች ሁሉ ምስጋናዬ ይድረስ። https://t.co/YRN2WtsRYO

በዓመቱ ማብቂያ ለሚካሄደው ብሔራዊ የችግኝ ተከላ መርሐ ግብር በኦሮሚያ ክልል የሚደረገውን የችግኝ ማፍላት ዝግጅት ዛሬ ጠዋት ተመልክቻለሁ። ለመጪው ክረምት የ#አረንጓዴ ዐሻራ ስራ በክልሉ 3.5 ቢሊዮን የተለያዩ ችግኞች እና 1.1 ቢሊዮን የቡና ችግኝ 1/2 https://t.co/hdETsgu8Ds
ይህ የሚያመለክተን የአርሶ አደሮቻችን ህይወት በሙሉ አቅም እገዛ ከተደረገለት በአጭር ጊዜ ውስጥ ለውጥ ሊያመጣ እንደሚችል አንድ ትልቅ ማሳያ ሆኖ አግኝቼዋለሁ ። 4/4
በመዝራት ፣ በመቀጠል በመስኖ በመታገዝ ስንዴ በመዝራታቸው አሁን የደረሰውን ማሳ ለማየት ችለናል ፤ በመቀጠል ለአትክልት ዝርያዎች ዝግጅታቸውን አጠናቀው በመትከል በአመት ለሶስተኛ ጊዜ ማምረት እንደሚችሉ በተግባር እያረጋግጡ ይገኛሉ። 3/4 https://t.co/Za8SuHir3G
የበጋ ስንዴ ምርት በማየቴ እጅግ ተደስቻለሁ፡፡ ይህ ሥራ ተጠናክሮ እንዲቀጥልና  በሌሎች አካባቢም ላይ መስፋፋት እንዲኖርበት የሁሉም ርብርብ ያስፈልጋል፡፡  በተጨማሪ በአመት ሶስት ግዜ ማምረት እንደሚችልም ተረድቻለሁ ። ጤፍን በክረምት 2/4
ዛሬ በኦሮሚያ ክልል አድአ ወረዳ በነበረኝ ቆይታ ያስተዋልኩት እና እጅጉን ያስደሰተኝ ጉዳይ አርሶ አደሮቻችን በ150 ሄክታር ላይ በክላስተር ማምረታቸውን ተመልክቻለው፡፡ ከውጪ ሀገር የምናስገባውን ስንዴ የሚተካ በሐገራችን ለመጀመሪያ ግዜ1/4 https://t.co/kq1F4u8EF6
በተለይም ሴቶችን በዚህ ልክ ብናግዝ ጥንካሬያቸውን በተግባር እንደሚያሳዩ ያረጋገጥንበት አስደሳች የመስክ ጉብኝት ነበር።3/3 https://t.co/bbzyRTQ9ve

tweets.text: A private sector led edible oil agro-industrial cluster is emerging in Bure Damot and Debre Makos in Gojjam. 3/4 https://t.co/ETzi7sPq5N

Yet, Ethiopia is one of the largest importers of edible oil in the world market, where more than 95% of domestic demand is met through imports—the average year import bill for edible oil is more than USD 400m. 2/4 https://t.co/09fUfg3GlL
Oilseeds are one of the principal sources of Ethiopia’s export earnings, and more than 3 million small-holders are involved in its production and distribution. 1/4 https://t.co/Kln4hf95nJ

data.text: If we work collectively, the #COVID19 pandemic will come to pass. Of what we can overcome, we need not believe it will consume us. We will share what we have; we will crossover. Have no doubt that this too shall pass!

No one takes out what they do not already have. So is the heart. It receives what it gives out. To receive, one must first learn to give. We cannot be generous whilst thinking of losses. This is why we can only narrate tales of wealth to be prosperous,rather than that of poverty.

data.text: Today we discussed and passed the bylaws for the newly merged Party. The three day discussions were concluded in a transparent and democratic manner bringing leaders of the Party closer, which I am quite pleased with.

Marii murteessaa Dhimma walitti makamuu Paartii irratti kaleessa itti fufuun har'as kallattii sagantaa ijoo Paartii walitti makamuurratti mari'anneerra. Sagantaa paartiirratti mari'annee raggaasisuu keenya gammachuu guddaannan isin beeksisa.
ትላንት ካደረግነው የፓርቲ ውሕደት ወሳኝ ውይይት በመቀጠል ዛሬም በሚዋሐደዉ ፓርቲ ቁልፍ የፕሮግራም አቅጣጫዎች ዙሪያ ተመካክረናል:: በፓርቲ ፕሮግራሙ ላይ ተወያይተን ማጽደቃችንን ሳበሥር በታላቅ ደስታ ነው::

Following our decisive EPRDF merger discussions held yesterday, our continued discussions today addressed key issues related to the programs of the newly merged party. I am pleased to share the program is approved.
በተጨማሪም ኅብረ ብሔራዊነትን የሚያጸና፣ አካታችነትንና ፍትሐዊ ዉክልናን የሚያረጋግጥ ሁነኛ አቅጣጫ ነዉ:: የፓርቲው ውሕደት ሀገራዊ አንድነትን ከኅብረ ብሔራዊነት ጋር አስተሣሥሮ ለመጓዝ ዕድል የሚሰጥ ይሰጣል።
ዛሬ የፓርቲ ዉሕደቱን በተመለከተ ያደረግነዉ ወሳኝ ስብሰሰባ አመርቂ ዉጤት አስመዝግቧል:: ዉሕደቱ የኢትዮጵያን የፌዴራል ሥርዓት ይበልጥ የሚያጠናክር፣ ተሰሚነት ላልነበራቸዉ አጋር ድርጅቶች እኩል ድምጽ የሚሰጥ ነዉ።
ልዩነቶችን ለመፍታት ብቸኛው መንገድ ውይይት ነው። ዛሬ ከተፎካካሪ ፖርቲዎች ጋር የነበረን ውይይት ተስፋ ሰጪ ነበር። ሁላችንም የተጎዱ ማኅበረሰቦችን የመደገፍና የማረጋጋት ሚና እንድንጫወት ጥሪ አቀርባለሁ።
I was pleased to meet with @melindagates earlier today to discuss further collaborations. Thank you for your continued support to Ethiopia.
የትምህርት ተቋሞቻችን እውቅት ማሳደጊያና የጥልቅ እሳቤ ክህሎት ማበልጸጊያ ናቸው:: ተማሪዎቻቸውም ሀሳብን በማፍለቅና በጤነኛ ሙግት የተራራቁ ማኅበረሰቦች ለማቀራረብ ድልድይ እንጂ የመለያየት ወኪሎች መሆን አይገባቸውም::
To all followers of the Muslim faith, I wish you a happy Maulid al-Nabi.

ለመላው የእስልምና እምነት ተከታዮች በሙሉ መልካም የመውሊድ አል ነቢ በዓል እንዲሆንላችሁ እመኛለሁ::

Hordoftoota Amantaa Musliimaa Maraaf: baga ayyaana Moolidaa, guyyaa dhaloota Nabi Mahammad tiin (S.A.W) isin gahe. 
Ayyaana Gaarii isiniif hawwa!
Congratulations to my friend @JustinTrudeau for your reelection victory. Wishing you all the best ahead.

entity.name: At least 67 killed as Typhoon Hagibis slams Japan, NHK reports
entity.description: The powerful typhoon swept through Japan on Saturday and brought heavy rain that caused floods and landslides, killing at least 56 people, according to NHK. Officials have ordered the evacuation of hundreds of thousands of people as torrential rains caused some rivers to exceed the flood level.
